reviews.review:
Let's take a look to my favourite game : 
- DBD has best DLC's (One of them are based on films and I'm a fan);
- It takes short time to get in a match;
- Perfect game to play with friends;
- Best Halloween,Christmas moments,and special events.
- I like the perks mechanics.
- It's very fun to play survivor with friends
In my opinion you need to buy this game and vote it for THE STEAM AWARDS because it is 10 euros on sale and I have great memories,and great moments in game right now.
It is worth ? : 10/10
